Fill in the Crucible Username and Password in the settings tab and then click on 'Start Dump' button below to begin the data dump. The generated Excel file will be made visible once the data dumping is complete. The last tab 'Log' the progress of the data dumping steps.
Additional Hints for settings 1. CrucibleProjectName : You may also adapt the project name as per requirement. 2. ReviewUrl : By default all the Closed reviews are processed. In case you need to dump all open and closed reviews, change the word 'allClosedReviews' to 'allReviews' 3. AcceptStrings : If you need to add or remove new strings in comments to be parsed to check whether the comment is accepted, you may change this parameter.
